349
00:21:54,384 --> 00:21:56,477
Well, we can't be outdone.

350
00:21:57,306 --> 00:21:59,852
What do you mean?

351
00:22:01,446 --> 00:22:07,235
Actually, you know, this past Sunday was the first date for me and Maki as well, a memorable one.

352
00:22:09,602 --> 00:22:10,579
I'm sorry.

353
00:22:11,181 --> 00:22:13,102
So did you have a mental strip down too?

354
00:22:13,127 --> 00:22:14,384
