355
00:22:14,696 --> 00:22:20,876
I've been trying to get him to take his clothes off too.
He seems to have developed a sense of shame, and he doesn't want to take off his clothes.

356
00:22:20,999 --> 00:22:23,242
That's a little weird.

357
00:22:23,351 --> 00:22:27,867
Anyway, let's go skating together.
I'll call him and ask him.

358
00:22:29,179 --> 00:22:32,593
Can you come over?
I made you one of my good ones.

359
00:22:32,757 --> 00:22:33,789
