366
00:23:00,781 --> 00:23:03,531
If I like someone, I should tell him right away.

367
00:23:03,734 --> 00:23:05,609
He's a sensible guy.

368
00:23:05,874 --> 00:23:07,804
He's going to investigate before he approves.

369
00:23:08,304 --> 00:23:09,085
He's going to investigate me?

370
00:23:09,437 --> 00:23:11,882
Teach me,Maki.

371
00:23:16,210 --> 00:23:17,249
Teach me,Maki.

372
00:23:18,234 --> 00:23:21,249
Ready? 1.2.

