You are stupid.

376
00:23:29,539 --> 00:23:30,921
You hit her.

377
00:23:32,390 --> 00:23:33,874
What's the hell?

378
00:23:34,406 --> 00:23:35,679
What?

379
00:23:36,078 --> 00:23:37,257
What's wrong?

380
00:23:37,703 --> 00:23:40,476
