All right, let's get loud.

381
00:23:42,007 --> 00:23:43,843
Come on!

382
00:23:48,815 --> 00:23:50,768
Please wait over there.

383
00:23:50,793 --> 00:23:52,026
Let's go.

384
00:23:52,627 --> 00:23:55,495
Bring it on!

385
00:24:01,164 --> 00:24:02,601
Are you alright?

386
00:24:02,969 --> 00:24:03,484
I'm alright.

387
00:24:04,125 --> 00:24:05,539
Where are you going?

388
00:24:06,297 --> 00:24:06,601
Oh.

389
00:24:06,626 --> 00:24:07,109
What's wrong?

390
00:24:07,281 --> 00:24:08,219
I only have 50 yen.

391
00:24:09,140 --> 00:24:12,163
My bag was taken by Kasumi...

392
00:24:12,188 --> 00:24:14,594
Please drive as far as you can go for 50 yen.

393
00:24:15,547 --> 00:24:17,930
Please go to Higashi Ginza

394
00:24:19,755 --> 00:24:22,646
