405
00:24:56,518 --> 00:24:58,174
Nice to meet you.

406
00:24:58,456 --> 00:25:03,370
I've always wanted to meet you.

407
00:25:03,395 --> 00:25:05,643
I have a phone call from Kasumi Fujisawa.

408
00:25:05,668 --> 00:25:07,331
I'll be back in a minute.

409
00:25:07,753 --> 00:25:09,058
Please come in.

410
00:25:09,714 --> 00:25:14,542
I was worried about you.
How come you didn't have any money?

411
00:25:15,929 --> 00:25:19,523
Are you with Maki?
Have fun.

412
00:25:20,937 --> 00:25:23,453
We're just leaving.

413
00:25:23,922 --> 00:25:27,906
I'm trying to think of something to say to Mother, so I'm having Kei-chan come up with an excuse.

414
00:25:42,739 --> 00:25:44,246
Hello, tickets?

415
00:25:44,364 --> 00:25:46,223
I'm just buying the program.

416
00:25:53,309 --> 00:25:57,192
Suppose you were with Ochiyo.
It's like that melodroma you hate.

417
00:26:07,713 --> 00:26:09,424
You know her?

418
00:26:10,205 --> 00:26:10,720
Yes.

419
00:26:12,947 --> 00:26:13,580
Hi.

420
00:26:16,999 --> 00:26:18,585
I'll take you home.

421
00:26:21,412 --> 00:26:23,032
Is she one of the your girls?

422
00:26:23,192 --> 00:26:23,739
Kind of.

423
00:26:25,297 --> 00:26:26,551
She's still looking.

424
00:26:26,576 --> 00:26:27,404
I don't care.

425
00:26:33,453 --> 00:26:34,306
Welcome.

426
00:26:35,113 --> 00:26:37,526
I'll give you some gifts.

427
00:26:37,747 --> 00:26:40,647
Thanks.
Kasumi wouldn't visit you?

428
00:26:42,001 --> 00:26:45,008
She said she was visiting you from college on Saturday.

429
00:26:45,796 --> 00:26:47,089
Maybe we've crossed paths.

430
00:26:48,126 --> 00:26:50,246
She told me she visited you often these days.

431
00:26:51,319 --> 00:26:51,946
No?

432
00:26:52,660 --> 00:26:55,707
Yes she is vising me often.

433
00:26:57,117 --> 00:27:00,644
This pickle... a long, thin cucumber... pickled with sake lees or something...

434
00:27:01,004 --> 00:27:04,124
This is awesome.

435
00:27:37,125 --> 00:27:39,225
