465
00:29:38,412 --> 00:29:39,212
What are you looking at?

466
00:29:40,184 --> 00:29:41,924
That fountain.

467
00:29:42,171 --> 00:29:42,877
Same here.

468
00:29:47,257 --> 00:29:49,484
