469
00:29:49,604 --> 00:29:50,897
I don't wanna talk about her.

470
00:29:50,922 --> 00:29:54,125
If you want to get away from that woman, there is a way.

471
00:29:54,592 --> 00:29:55,678
You're going to do something.

472
00:29:56,666 --> 00:29:59,592
I feel sorry for her at the time, but it's the best way to give up.

