487
00:30:40,354 --> 00:30:43,067
I don't know what it felt like.

488
00:30:43,693 --> 00:30:44,326
Did you feel good?

489
00:30:44,846 --> 00:30:47,372
I don't know, but it felt like I was getting hot and my body was evaporating.

490
00:30:47,552 --> 00:30:48,232
Oh my god.

491
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:53,747
That's good to know,
