492
00:30:54,267 --> 00:30:55,060
Next?

493
00:30:55,406 --> 00:30:58,946
Talk to me!
I'm going to use it as a reference.

494
00:31:01,943 --> 00:31:04,069
Then what happened next?

495
00:31:04,116 --> 00:31:06,429
Then we went to eat okonomiyaki.

496
00:31:07,613 --> 00:31:10,386
I'm going to make an offer to your father tomorrow.

497
00:31:10,411 --> 00:31:11,196
Don't do that.

498
00:31:11,296 --> 00:31:13,376
Why?
Keep it until you finish college?

499
00:31:13,469 --> 00:31:16,043
I don't care to quit college.

500
00:31:16,276 --> 00:31:19,710
I promised my dad I'd tell him if I ever met someone I liked.

501
00:31:19,776 --> 00:31:20,583
Then do it.

502
00:31:21,084 --> 00:31:22,904
That's where he'll look into it.

503
00:31:23,477 --> 00:31:24,424
Don't scare me.

504
00:31:24,577 --> 00:31:25,391
Really.

505
00:31:26,980 --> 00:31:27,567
What are you going to do?

506
00:31:27,660 --> 00:31:29,774
Are you serious?

507
00:31:29,867 --> 00:31:31,087
Of course I am.

508
00:31:31,112 --> 00:31:33,287
I don't know what to do.

509
00:31:34,346 --> 00:31:35,706
Leave it to me.

510
00:31:36,461 --> 00:31:37,341
Yes.

511
00:31:37,545 --> 00:31:38,732
In exchange, I have a condition.

512
00:31:38,757 --> 00:31:39,240
What?

513
00:31:39,873 --> 00:31:44,379
From now on, you will not hide anything from me, either before or after our marriage.

514
00:31:44,639 --> 00:31:46,472
